On that note, I hope the rest of the wizard class tuning isnt a bunch of level 39 spells.  Don't get me wrong, Im glad harvest was added but jeezus, that was after I had already hit 50 and suffered without it forever.   The same for consussion.  There needs to be lower level tuning, but everyone will apreciate tweaks on the high end more in the long run.<br>
<br>
I don't really get the people saying Wizards are useless, and I hope we don't deteriorate all these threads to that.  Post 50 I think we do start to see improvements.  Just go out to Timm Deep and watch the wizzies quad kite raptors for hours on end and you will see what I mean.<br>
<br>
Believe it or not, wizzies are one of the *MOST* needed classes for the uber mobs.  Try taking down Trak, Serv, Talon or Gore without any wizards.<br>
<br>
True, we may not have the most efficient, fastest casting DD's that we prolly should - but at least we can hit the Dragons and uber mobs =)<br>
<br>
