<br>
I think the problem is, verant cant nerf us like other classes.. ok will go in to more detail.. Can they take hp? Well yes then can, but no one would play the class, we have little hp as is, equip not withstanding. Ac? dont have much in those regards either, therefor it to cant really be taken away. What can they take from us to offset the amount of Damage we should do? Thats the problem i think, but id be willing to bet no one up in that corpriate office will admit it. They have to have a pro/con reasoning for balance, but if a class has little, if you take that, it has nothing, so how do you better a class that cant be balanced by what their methods are... simply put, you cant. (not sure if that sounds right but its a generalzation)<br>
