<br>
I am not saying wizards don't need work on their DD capabilities (the removal of the 32k cap in SoV really hurt wizards)...I am only trying to point out the fact that wizards can be group friendly if they actually try.  Wizards aren't a one-sided class and shouldn't be treated as one.<br>
